args.new_string:
// Package companion is the primary v1 adapter: a WebSocket fanout to
// browser companion apps that every participant opens alongside their
// existing video tool (Zoom / Meet / Teams / in-person).
//
// Capabilities: GainScope=None, GainPolarity=Advisory. This adapter can
// only request — visibility (the bid heat-map) + countdown nudges are
// the entire enforcement. For mute-only hard enforcement, layer the
